com.restermans

Class PriorityQueueB<E extends java.lang.Comparable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.restermans.PriorityQueueB<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements held in this collection

    public class PriorityQueueB<E extends java.lang.Comparable>
extends java.lang.Object
    An unbounded priority queue based on a priority heap. The elements of the priority queue are ordered according to their natural ordering A priority queue relying on natural ordering also does not permit insertion of non-comparable objects (doing so may result in ClassCastException).
